sequenceDiagram
    participant App as Python app
    participant Wrapper as Config
    participant CDLL as _native CDLL
    participant Bridge as bridge.cpp
    participant Pool as HandlePool
    participant Obj as Config C++ object

    App->>Wrapper: Config.create(30, url, True)
    Wrapper->>CDLL: config_create(...)
    CDLL->>Bridge: extern C call
    Bridge->>Pool: store(unique_ptr Config)
    Pool-->>Bridge: handle id e.g. 1
    Bridge-->>Wrapper: int64_t handle
    Wrapper-->>App: Config(handle=1)

    App->>Wrapper: config.process()
    Wrapper->>CDLL: config_process(1)
    CDLL->>Bridge: extern C call
    Bridge->>Pool: get_as Config handle 1
    Pool->>Obj: static_cast Config*
    Obj-->>Bridge: process result
    Bridge-->>App: int 147

    App->>Wrapper: close or __del__
    Wrapper->>CDLL: handle_release(1)
    CDLL->>Bridge: extern C call
    Bridge->>Pool: release(1)
    Pool->>Obj: unique_ptr destructor
